    "title": {
      "rendered": "6 Must-Download Mobile Apps for Good"
    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-22000\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/Mobile-Apps-for-Good-Facebook-300x300.jpg?resize=300%2C300\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/Mobile-Apps-for-Good-Facebook.jpg?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/Mobile-Apps-for-Good-Facebook.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/Mobile-Apps-for-Good-Facebook.jpg?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/Mobile-Apps-for-Good-Facebook.jpg?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/Mobile-Apps-for-Good-Facebook.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" />Thus far, nonprofits have struggled to create mobile apps that their donors and supporters want to use. They don&#8217;t have the financial resources or staff expertise necessary and as a result, app stores are lacking in apps that inspire people to do good.</p>\n<p>Now 11 years after the launch of the first iPhone, social enterprises and socially-responsible businesses are finding creative ways to contribute to the mobile app economy with apps that combine lifestyle with social good. For 2018, these are the must-download mobile apps to explore.</p>\n<hr />\n<h1 style=\"text-align: left;\">1. Reach<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.reachmobile.no\">reachmobile.no</a></h1>\n<p>The Reach app encourages users to explore the world by sharing photos and videos of their travels or visits to local landmarks and natural sites. Engaging with ads earns users Recoins that can then be donated to their favorite nonprofits.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.reachmobile.no\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-21974\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/Reach.jpg?resize=600%2C292\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"292\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/Reach.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/Reach.jpg?resize=300%2C146&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1>2. Stance<br />\n<a href=\"http://takeastance.us\">takeastance.us</a></h1>\n<p>Stance delivers voice messages straight to a\u00a0congressperson&#8217;s voicemail and if he or she\u2019s voicemail is full, Stance keeps calling until it\u2019s available.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://takeastance.us\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-21977\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/STANCE.jpg?resize=600%2C346\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"346\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/STANCE.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/STANCE.jpg?resize=300%2C173&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1>3. MaximusLife<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.maximuslife.com/challenges/\">maximuslife.com</a></h1>\n<p>Join a MaximusLife Challenge to walk 10,000 steps a day, give up salt for a week, do yoga three times weekly, etc. and if you succeed, a donation is made to charity on your behalf.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.maximuslife.com/challenges/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-21988\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/maximus.jpg?resize=600%2C338\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/maximus.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/maximus.jpg?resize=300%2C169&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1>4. Gone for Good<br />\n<a href=\"https://goneforgood.org.uk\">goneforgood.org.uk</a></h1>\n<p>Take a photo of your unwanted goods, schedule a pick up, and a charity will collect your goods directly from your door.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://goneforgood.org.uk\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-21986\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/Gone-for-Good.jpg?resize=600%2C349\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"349\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/Gone-for-Good.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/Gone-for-Good.jpg?resize=300%2C175&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1>5. GiveTide<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.givetide.com\">givetide.com</a></h1>\n<p>Users add their credit card info to the app, GiveTide rounds up all transactions to the nearest dollar, and then users give the money raised to their favorite nonprofits with a single tap.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.givetide.com\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-21984\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/GiveTide2.jpg?resize=600%2C358\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"358\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/GiveTide2.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/GiveTide2.jpg?resize=300%2C179&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1>6. DriveSafe<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.thedrivesafeapp.com\">thedrivesafeapp.com</a></h1>\n<p>The DriveSafe app\u00a0sets up auto-responders for messaging apps and texting and turns on automatically\u00a0as soon as you get in your car.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.thedrivesafeapp.com\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-21993\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/drivesafe.jpg?resize=600%2C344\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"344\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/drivesafe.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/drivesafe.jpg?resize=300%2C172&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<hr />\n<h2>The <strong><a href=\"http://techreport.ngo\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">2018 Global NGO Technology Report</a></strong> summarizes how NGOs use web and email communications, online fundraising tools, social media, mobile technology, and data management and security software.</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://techreport.ngo\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-21997 size-full\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/For-Blog.jpg?resize=600%2C315\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"315\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/For-Blog.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/For-Blog.jpg?resize=300%2C158&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n",
      "protected": false
    },
